            <thetext>If you are using RTL text input (Arabic etc.), a padding of 0 (padding-right/left) breaks the cursor rendering on Internet Explorer 9/10. 

If _createContentElement in qx.ui.form.AbstractField got padding and margin removed, there is no issue in cursor rendering anymore.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
